column1: Log exposure and analysis levels (Luminance (Y) channel for color images)
'Densities' are -log10(normalized pixel levels) for Y R G and B channels; RGBY means and medians are in pixels (max 255).
Noise (normalized to 1.5 density range and maximum) and f-stop noise and SNR (scene-referenced). This table changed in Imatest 3.9: added line and fields.
S/N (signal/noise) and SNR(dB) (20*log10(signal/noise)) for each patch
Dynamic Range in f-stops (EV): total and for quality levels corresponding to SNR = 1/f-stop noise
